\section*{Preparation of Vaccine Service Delivery Site/Facility.}
- Should be clean, and not directly exposed to sunlight, rain or dust.
- Should be easily accessible.
- It should be quiet enough for the health worker to carry out health education.
- There should be necessary furniture e.g. a table and chairs.
