\section*{Water.}
- Is composed of two hydrogens and one oxygen per molecule of water.
- Essential constituent of food and human body.

\section*{Functions.}
- Acts as a carrier of nutrients in foods.
- Maintains the structure of the food material.
- Acts as a reactant and a reaction medium for many biological reactions.
